textBeforeTable: February Suitable for kids of all ages and their families Our exciting Hands on History programs answer these and many more questions. You will have the opportunity to try on uniforms, handle real items and hear the incredible stories of Australian men and women in war. What jobs do servicement and women do? What do they wear? What do they eat? Orientation Gallery 11 am and 2pm Hands on History There are no upcoming dates for this event.
